INSERT INTO `tgb_posts` VALUES(207, 1, '2011-10-20 17:29:45', '2011-10-20 22:29:45', '<h2>About Nossi</h2>\r\nFrom the website, "Nossi College of Art is a small, private, professional college with a friendly atmosphere. We are dedicated to developing students into working professionals in the vast and exciting business of visual communications. Nossi College of Art is special because we train students in a unique combination of methods." -Nossi (Vatandoost, President/CEO)\r\n<h2>The Project</h2>\r\nNossi needed something artistic, creative, fun and had the ability to draw in youth and parents alike. WordPress helped us provide for with a savvy events calendar, heavy search engine optimization, a clean Google sitemap structure, a news and blog section and a multi-album photo gallery. The whole project was backed by an intense reporting campaign and specific promotion tracking and reporting.', 'Nossi College of Art', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '194-revision-4', '', '', '2011-10-20 17:29:45', '2011-10-20 22:29:45', '', 194, 'http://thomasgbennett.com/194-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `tgb_posts` VALUES(208, 1, '2011-10-20 17:23:40', '2011-10-20 22:23:40', '<h2>About The Outpost Armory</h2>\r\nFrom the website, "We opened The Outpost Armory to provide both the novice and expert alike with the best products and service available anywhere. We strive to provide more selection than the big chain stores without compromising the knowledge and the service you should expect from a small gun shop. We not only offer a place to purchase firearms, ammunition and accessories, but also provide a community for conscientious citizens." -The Outpost Amory\r\n<h2>The Project</h2>\r\nThe web store, or e-commerce platform, for TOA is built using Magento Commerce. With almost 40,000 products and hundreds of categories all being brought in dynamically from an external source, the customization on this project was massive. While the client has full control of the site, the automation of product and images loading is a painless process allowed by several custom imports.\r\n\r\nA few custom features:\r\n\r\nThe FFL Locator allows you to pinpoint your location and choose where you want your weapon to be shipped to. It''s also smart enough to check and see if you have an item in your cart that requires an FFL.\r\n\r\nThe top sellers page allows for both actual best sellers and client-suggested items to display. A custom product product collection was built to only incorporate appropriate products and their information to help speed up the load-time for the user.\r\n\r\nThe special orders page uses a custom Magento form to place specific requests.', 'The Outpost Armory', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '192-revision-2', '', '', '2011-10-20 17:23:40', '2011-10-20 22:23:40', '', 192, 'http://thomasgbennett.com/192-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `tgb_posts` VALUES(209, 1, '2011-10-20 17:12:41', '2011-10-20 22:12:41', '<h2>About the Belle Meade Winery</h2>\r\nAs the premier thoroughbred racing and breeding farm in the South for over a century, Belle Meade Plantation was the center of hospitality in the 1800s. Five United States presidents have enjoyed the renowned hospitality of the Harding and Jackson families, and the 5,400 acres that made up the Plantation were home to some of the greatest horses in racing history. The Plantation’s hospitality always included homemade wine, with the use of its many wild and domestic grapevines. In November 2009, the opening of The Winery at Belle Meade Plantation ensured the long tradition of hospitality would continue.\r\n<h2>The Project</h2>\r\nA simple, slick but yet creative solution was necessary for this project. The result was a one-page, scrolling navigation that allowed the content to flow in an elegant and unique manner. While the appearance of the website is a simple solution, the backend allows for full user control, adding wine bottles and content as well as a fully customizable blog and recipe section.', 'Belle Meade Winery', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '190-revision-2', '', '', '2011-10-20 17:12:41', '2011-10-20 22:12:41', '', 190, 'http://thomasgbennett.com/190-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `tgb_posts` VALUES(210, 1, '2011-10-20 17:02:59', '2011-10-20 22:02:59', '<h2>About Semper Fi Fund</h2>\r\nThe Injured Marine Semper Fi Fund is a 501(c)(3) nonprofit set up to provide immediate financial support for injured and critically ill members of the U.S. Armed Forces and their families. We direct urgently needed resources to post 9-11 Marines and Sailors, as well as members of the Army, Air Force or Coast Guard who serve in support of Marine forces.\r\n<h2>The Project</h2>\r\nThe Fund had an extremely large website when they arrived at <a href="http://iostudio.com" target="_blank">iostudio</a> for help. A clean, fluid, elegant design and a revamped, organized backend because the fore-front focus. WordPress helped us provide for with a savvy events calendar, heavy search engine optimization, a clean Google sitemap structure, a news and blog section and a multi-album photo gallery.', 'Semper Fi Fund', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '188-revision-2', '', '', '2011-10-20 17:02:59', '2011-10-20 22:02:59', '', 188, 'http://thomasgbennett.com/188-revision-2/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `tgb_posts` VALUES(211, 1, '2011-10-20 16:55:23', '2011-10-20 21:55:23', 'About Mockingbird Musicians\r\n\r\nWith three classical music degrees and with Chris'' experience playing with the Broadway show <a href="http://www.raintribute.com/" target="_blank"><em>Rain: A Tribute to the Beatles</em></a>, Mockingbird has the versatility, contacts and experience to bring you the best music in town. Weddings, events - no problem. Getting any combination of instrumentalists or vocalists for any type of event is the specialty. Whether you want a string quartet, bluegrass band, or just a singer and a pianist, they can hook you up!\r\n\r\nThe Project\r\n\r\nThis project started with a small website and big dreams in mind. Chris and Nikki needed a slick design and a backend optimized and ready for their SEO needs. The website contains a blog as well as the ability to edit all the pages and images.', 'Mockingbird Musicians', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '181-revision-5', '', '', '2011-10-20 16:55:23', '2011-10-20 21:55:23', '', 181, 'http://thomasgbennett.com/181-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
INSERT INTO `tgb_posts` VALUES(212, 1, '2011-10-20 16:47:58', '2011-10-20 21:47:58', '<h2>About Kimber</h2>\r\nKimber was founded with the singular purpose of building fine sporting firearms, better even than classics from the golden age of American gunmaking. Modern manufacturing techniques would be embraced and used to advantage, but assembly, fit and finish could only depend on practiced hands. There would be no compromise in features, materials or performance.\r\n\r\nKimber quality has led to unprecedented demand. Organizations like the USA Shooting Team, LAPD™ SWAT and United States Marines assigned to Central Command chose Kimber. American shooters did too, in a big way, and Kimber has become the world''s largest producer of 1911 pistols.\r\n<h2>The Project</h2>\r\nA chic, sexy design with all the ins and outs, a robust, expandable website and CMS that could house hundred of products and pages, the ability to upload images, videos, edit text right from the website and house a dealer-database with hundreds of dealers - believe it or not, a short list of the items that went into this project. Look at the photos and spend some time browsing the website for yourself.\r\n<h2>Web Store</h2>\r\nBuilt using the popular <a href="http://www.dotnetnuke.com/" target="_blank">Dot Net Nuke</a> e-commerce platform, this site was skinned to be as pretty as the actual website. The products are being pulled in internally based on their inventory.', 'Kimber America', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '173-revision-6', '', '', '2011-10-20 16:47:58', '2011-10-20 21:47:58', '', 173, 'http://thomasgbennett.com/173-revision-6/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
