INSERT INTO `tgb_posts` VALUES(230, 1, '2011-10-20 22:10:21', '2011-10-21 03:10:21', '<h2>About Nossi</h2>\r\nFrom the website, "Nossi College of Art is a small, private, professional college with a friendly atmosphere. We are dedicated to developing students into working professionals in the vast and exciting business of visual communications. Nossi College of Art is special because we train students in a unique combination of methods." -Nossi (Vatandoost, President/CEO)\r\n<h2>The Project</h2>\r\n<img class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-206" title="Nossi Gallery" src="http://thomasgbennett.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Screen-shot-2011-10-20-at-10.09.08-PM-460x341.png" alt="Nossi Gallery" width="460" height="341" />Nossi needed something artistic, creative, fun and had the ability to draw in youth and parents alike. WordPress helped us provide for with a savvy events calendar, heavy search engine optimization, a clean Google sitemap structure, a news and blog section and a multi-album photo gallery. The whole project was backed by an intense reporting campaign and specific promotion tracking and reporting.', 'Nossi College of Art', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '194-revision-5', '', '', '2011-10-20 22:10:21', '2011-10-21 03:10:21', '', 194, 'http://thomasgbennett.com/194-revision-5/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
